quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  55,46,"And to who feared His Lord`s place/position , two treed gardens"
  55,47,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,48,of (the two treed gardens) have branches
  55,49,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,50,"In them (B) (are) two water springs/wells, they (B) flow"
  55,51,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,52,"In them (B) (are) from every/each fruits, a pair/couple/two kinds"
  55,53,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,54,"Leaning/reclining on on spreads/beds its lining/interior (is) from brocade , and the two treed gardens` harvest (fruits is) near"
  55,55,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,56,"In them (B) (are) confining the eyes, (they) were not touched (by) a human before them, and nor Jinn"
  55,57,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,58,"As if/though they (F) are corundum/hardest mineral after diamond (rubies/sapphires/ topazes), and the corals"
  55,59,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,60,"Is the goodness` reimbursement , except the goodness"
  55,61,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,62,And from other than them (B) two treed gardens
  55,63,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,64,(are) blackish green and fragrant
  55,65,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,66,"In them (B) (are) two water springs/wells, (B) flowing/gushing"
  55,67,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,68,"In them (B) (are) fruits, and palm trees, and pomegranate"
  55,69,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,70,In them (B) (are) very beautiful good/generous
  55,71,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,72,Dilated pupils (very beautiful) confined/limited in the tents
  55,73,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,74,"(They) were not touched (by) a human before them, and nor Jinn"
  55,75,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,76,Leaning/relining on green carpets/pillows/silk and very beautiful fine carpets
  55,77,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,78,"Blessed (is) your Lord`s name, (owner) of the glory/splendor and the honour/generosity"